WEBVTT

00:00:01.348 --> 00:00:03.427
("Also sprach Zarathustra,"
Richard Strauss)

00:00:03.451 --> 00:00:06.363
Nick Selby: If you want to change
the world, you can do that.

00:00:06.387 --> 00:00:08.682
If you want to build the Iron Man suit,

00:00:08.706 --> 00:00:09.942
you can do that.

00:00:10.419 --> 00:00:12.071
We can do that!

00:00:14.315 --> 00:00:17.705
Adam Grant: You know an inspiring
commencement speech when you hear one.

00:00:17.729 --> 00:00:19.045
It's electrifying.

00:00:19.069 --> 00:00:20.220
You feel so pumped up

00:00:20.244 --> 00:00:23.156
that you're ready to paint
the ceiling of the Sistine Chapel,

00:00:23.180 --> 00:00:25.355
climb El Capitan without any ropes

00:00:25.379 --> 00:00:27.702
or build that Iron Man suit.

00:00:28.188 --> 00:00:31.895
As a professor, I've heard
quite a few graduation speeches.